Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}死に至る罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}犯しても次へ
