Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}増していく代償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}向かう先が地獄だとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}後悔なんてない Anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Fallin' fallin' down 暗闇へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:57.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But, never going back 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狼煙高く上げて Now dive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}煩悩なんてモノ Good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}性懲りも無く Fight 仲間と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Live to die another day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I won't run away from my sin no more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:10.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}何処までも抗って Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:13.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 超えていく 恐れずに Bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I'm not afraid, bring it on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if I'm drown in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}自分のチカラに変え Wipe out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 捻じ曲げる System
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I never ever follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:32.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今 立ち向かう and I'll defeat myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:20.33,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像人性一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你将凝视深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.24,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那里有七宗罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.07,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}当你踏入其中 你会发觉自己还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}踏入未知领域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:34.21,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}那些漂亮话 早就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.49,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人得以为人的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.07,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总是伴随着我们 对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.50,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}致命的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:42.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不要转移视线 赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:44.53,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只是向前 向前 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我必须再次取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.22,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}代价在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:48.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使前方是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.68,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也不再有任何后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.61,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坠落 坠落 堕入黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:57.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是 永远不回头 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.13,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}高举烽烟 然后潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.34,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}与烦恼说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:01.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惩前毖后 与伙伴一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:03.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}活着就是为了择日赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不再逃避我的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:10.07,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我将一直抗争下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:13.66,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 无畏地超越 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我不害怕 放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:18.21,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}即使我将陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:21.52,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}也要将其转化为我的力量 消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.65,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 扭曲这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.08,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.29,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我永远不会跟随它们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:32.25,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在 我将面对挑战并战胜自己
